                                                                                                                                    Clapton invite

              
	London, Feb. 26 (Reuters): North Korea has invited Eric Clapton to rock its capital, a spokesman for the communist countrys embassy in London said today.
    
	We have recently sent a letter to Claptons agent inviting him to Pyongyang for a concert, he said. He is a world famous guitarist. Eric Clapton is quite well known in the entire world. 
                                                                                
